The Project Lazarus server strives to bring many survival aspects from games such as Dayz and incorporate them into the Rust.

This server wipes every Thursday at 4 PM EST (Except for Force)

The server has the following modifications:
✦ 2x Resource Rate
✦ Half Smelt & Crafting Speeds
✦ Group Limit: 4
✦ All Tier 1 BPs Unlocked
✦ Improved Loot Tables
✦ Weekly Wipes

The server has the following custom mechanics:
✦ Ground Loot System: Loot items from the ground similar to DayZ.
✦ Monument Heists: Rob banks across the map and sell the gold bars at outposts.
✦ XP System: Redeem XP rewards by leveling up through farming and killing NPCs.
✦ Quest System: Complete various tasks to earn skill points which can be used to unlock perks.
✦ Drug System: Grow cocaine, heroine and cannabis at your base. You can then sell these drugs at the outpost once processed.
✦ Redemption System: Earn points for each kill on a geared player. These points can be used to unlock loot crates.
✦ Team Competitions: Earn points by doing various things. The team with the most points wins.
✦ Tiered Tool Cupboard: Players must upgrade their tool cupboard with cash to be able to upgrade to the next building tier.
✦ Player Run Marketplace: Players can access a marketplace through their mobile which allows them to earn cash where ever they are.
✦ DayZ Inspired Mechanics: Backpacks, parachutes, molotovs and drones.
